    <item>
      <title>欧盟考虑逐步禁止俄罗斯液化天然气和铝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/eu-considers-gradual-ban-on-russian-lng-and-aluminum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟正考虑对俄罗斯实施铝进口限制，并逐步淘汰俄罗斯的液化天然气，这是针对俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰实施的新一轮制裁措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/eu-considers-gradual-ban-on-russian-lng-and-aluminum</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉弗拉稀土公司获澳大利亚 2 亿澳元注资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/arafura-rare-earths-gets-a-200-million-in-funding-from-australia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉弗拉稀土有限公司将从澳大利亚国家重建基金获得 2 亿澳元（1.24 亿美元）资金，用于支持新建矿山和加工厂，这是西方国家在与中国进行战略竞争之际加强关键资源供应链的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/arafura-rare-earths-gets-a-200-million-in-funding-from-australia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
